tion.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Join.html#WickContraction.join\">join</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Join.html#WickContraction.join\">join</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/TimeContract.html#WickContraction.timeContract\">timeContract</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a>   <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/TimeContract.html#WickContraction.timeContract\">timeContract</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/UncontractedList.html#WickContraction.uncontractedListGet\">uncontractedListGet</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/TimeContract.html#WickContraction.timeContract\">timeContract</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a list `φs` of `𝓕.FieldOp`, a Wick contraction `φsΛ` of `φs`,\nand a Wick contraction `φsucΛ` of `[φsΛ]ᵘᶜ`,\n`(join φsΛ φsucΛ).sign • (join φsΛ φsucΛ).timeContract` is equal to the product of\n- `φsΛ.sign • φsΛ.timeContract` and\n- `φsucΛ.sign • φsucΛ.timeContract`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Join.html#WickContraction.join_sign_timeContract","kind":"theorem","line":432,"name":"WickContraction.join_sign_timeContract","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L432-L446"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Join.html#WickContraction.join_sign\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">join_sign</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/UncontractedList.html#WickContraction.uncontractedListGet\">uncontractedListGet</a></span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hc</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.GradingCompliant\">GradingCompliant</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Join.html#WickContraction.join\">join</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/UncontractedList.html#WickContraction.uncontractedListGet\">uncontractedListGet</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a list `φs` of `𝓕.FieldOp`, a grading compliant Wick contraction `φsΛ` of `φs`,\nand a Wick contraction `φsucΛ` of `[φsΛ]ᵘᶜ`, the following relation holds\n`(join φsΛ φsucΛ).sign = φsΛ.sign * φsucΛ.sign`.\n\nIn `φsΛ.sign` the sign is determined by starting with the contracted pair\nwhose first element occurs at the left-most position. This lemma manifests that this\nchoice does not matter, and that contracted pairs can be brought together in any order. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Join.html#WickContraction.join_sign","kind":"theorem","line":420,"name":"WickContraction.join_sign","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L420-L430"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Join.html#WickContraction.join_sign_induction\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">join_sign_induction</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/UncontractedList.html#WickContraction.uncontractedListGet\">uncontractedListGet</a></span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hc</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.GradingCompliant\">GradingCompliant</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hn</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Finset/Card.html#Finset.card\">card</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Join.html#WickContraction.join\">join</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/Basic.html#WickContraction.sign\">sign</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/UncontractedList.html#WickContraction.uncontractedListGet\">uncontractedListGet</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">φsucΛ</s